{
  "stem": "13096.6",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "So when we were taking, you know, these trains with the contingents of the refugees, they stop in Bologna.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And they put us there, you know, for temporary, for a couple of nights.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "While we were there-- and then we were telling our story that we-- because there were thousands of refugees that from one town of Italy going to another town, they bombarded their own houses.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "There were shelters all broken up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "And they were going all the direction to join the relatives-- one to the north, one to the south.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "And then we told our story that we were not like them, you know.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "We were different, these four people.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And we thought at the time we were the only survivors of the Auschwitz contingent.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "We didn't know what's happen to the other one.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "We thought we are only three people out of 2,000.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "And we don't know what to do.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "And then these people that speak Italian, they were all Italian, say, listen, the best thing for you, you are not Catholic.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "You are Jewish people.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There is a community we know in Bologna.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "There is a community of Jewish.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "You must go and speak to them, see what they tell advice to you.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "So we advised-- you know, we arrived there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And they give us the direction.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "We went by foot.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 51,
      "text": "In the meantime, while I was in, you know, with the Russian, my clothes, they were all, you know, torn and broken.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 52,
      "text": "I had exchanged them.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 53,
      "text": "The Russian has given me-- because I was singing, they were giving me a uniform of Russian, you know, soldier.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 54,
      "text": "I was-- it was September.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 55,
      "text": "It was very hot in Italy, Bologna especially.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 56,
      "text": "There is no sea there.",
      "word_count": 5
    }
  ],
